From the Infowars web site ::

On this, the Monday edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex talks with author and researcher Webster Tarpley about the faltering economy and the SEAL Team 6 fiasco. 

Alex also talks with author, journalist, and former managing director at Goldman Sachs, Nomi Prins, about the economy and the recent S&P downgrade of the United States. 

Critically acclaimed author and former State Department official Steve Pieczenik also talks about the SEAL Team 6 issue.
